Summarize a 5-page article about global warming. The article, “The Impact of Global Warming on the Environment and Global Economies”, examines the effects of global warming on the environment, animals and humans as well as the economic implications of climate change. It highlights how global warming affects organisms and ecosystems, the increasing cost of expanding resources to mitigate climate change, and rising water levels due to melting polar ice caps. The article also explores the extent to which developing countries must grapple with the need to adapt to global warming and its consequences.
